00:00:00.539 --> 00:00:04.700
Assign a Ringtone or Picture to a Contact
with the Samsung Galaxy S® III mini

00:00:04.700 --> 00:00:06.200
Welcome to AT&amp;T "How To" videos.

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:12.320
Today, we will show you how to assign a ringtone
or picture to a contact with the Samsung Galaxy

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:15.710
S® III mini.

00:00:15.710 --> 00:00:21.020
To begin, from the Home screen, tap Contacts.

00:00:21.020 --> 00:00:29.890
Next from the Contacts Tab, scroll to and
select the desired contact.

00:00:29.890 --> 00:00:34.590
Please Note: Graphics and ringtones cannot
be added to the contacts stored on your SIM

00:00:34.590 --> 00:00:38.180
card.

00:00:38.180 --> 00:00:43.620
Here tap the Pencil icon to edit.

00:00:43.620 --> 00:00:46.760
Let's review the options to personalize your
contacts.

00:00:46.760 --> 00:00:52.180
To add a graphic, tap Contacts.

00:00:52.180 --> 00:01:03.610
Tap 
the desired image option.

00:01:03.610 --> 00:01:09.920
Image allows you to select an existing image.

00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:14.970
Pictures by People allows you to select a
previously shared image from gallery.

00:01:14.970 --> 00:01:22.720
Select the Take picture option to take a new
photo.

00:01:22.720 --> 00:01:29.310
Here you can resize the photo as desired,
and then tap Done.

00:01:29.310 --> 00:01:34.260
The updated contact will be displayed.

00:01:34.260 --> 00:01:37.100
To Add a ringtone.

00:01:37.100 --> 00:01:44.409
Please Note: If using Easy mode, tap Add another
field, and then select Ringtone.

00:01:44.409 --> 00:01:49.760
Now, scroll to and tap Ringtone.

00:01:49.760 --> 00:01:55.170
Select the desired ringtone, and then tap
OK.

00:01:55.170 --> 00:01:58.390
The updated contact will be displayed.

00:01:58.390 --> 00:02:00.560
Tap Save.

00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:12.709
If further assistance is needed, please feel
free to visit our website at www.att.com/biz.

00:02:12.709 --> 00:02:17.799
First time users select your manufacturer
and model and then click Go.

00:02:17.799 --> 00:02:29.419
You will be able to access "Step by Step Tutorials"
or ask a question in our "AT&amp;T Business Community".

